titleNullable: Best Selling Game Boy Video Games
subtitleNullable: Best Selling Game Boy/Game Boy Color Video Games Data
descriptionNullable:
The Best Selling Game Boy Video Games dataset is a collection of data that includes information on the top selling games for the Game Boy console. This includes the title of the game, the developers, the publisher, the release date, the number of copies sold.

The data was collected from https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_best-selling_Game_Boy_video_games then cleaned for data analysis.

Tabular data includes:

- `Game`
- `Developer(s)`
- `Publisher`
- `Platform`
- `Release date`
- `Sales`
